{
  "name": "Healthcare Appointment Automation — SHOWCASE Architecture",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "sticky-overview",
      "name": "System Overview",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [-300, -200],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 4,
        "width": 560,
        "height": 340,
        "content": "## Healthcare Appointment Automation — SHOWCASE\n\n**MAXXAM AI — Architecture Reference**\n\nThis is a sanitized architecture showcase. All credentials are placeholders.\nThe full production system includes 5 additional chained workflows\n(AI voice qualification, ROI reporting, waitlist management, re-engagement sequences).\n\n**What this workflow handles:**\n1. Receives booking events from Cal.com via webhook\n2. Routes by event type: New Booking / Cancellation / No-Show\n3. Triggers appropriate communication sequence\n4. Logs all activity to Google Sheets\n\n**Stack:** Cal.com → n8n → Gmail + Twilio → Google Sheets\n\n> Book a discovery call: https://tinyurl.com/maxxam-call"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "trigger-webhook",
      "name": "Cal.com Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "position": [0, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "path": "{{ WEBHOOK_PATH }}",
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "responseMode": "lastNode",
        "options": {}
      },
      "webhookId": "healthcare-booking-webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-trigger",
      "name": "Trigger Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [-60, 160],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 5,
        "width": 280,
        "height": 120,
        "content": "### Step 1: Receive Booking Event\n\nCal.com sends a POST to this webhook on:\n- New booking\n- Cancellation\n- No-show (via manual trigger or Cal.com event)"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "set-config",
      "name": "System Config",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "position": [260, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "cfg-01",
              "name": "practiceEmail",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "{{ YOUR_PRACTICE_EMAIL }}"
            },
            {
              "id": "cfg-02",
              "name": "twilioFromNumber",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "{{ YOUR_TWILIO_NUMBER }}"
            },
            {
              "id": "cfg-03",
              "name": "bookingUrl",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "{{ YOUR_CAL_COM_BOOKING_URL }}"
            },
            {
              "id": "cfg-04",
              "name": "activitySheetId",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "{{ YOUR_GOOGLE_SHEET_ID }}"
            },
            {
              "id": "cfg-05",
              "name": "staffAlertEmail",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "{{ YOUR_STAFF_ALERT_EMAIL }}"
            },
            {
              "id": "cfg-06",
              "name": "sessionValue",
              "type": "number",
              "value": 150
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "typeVersion": 3.4
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-config",
      "name": "Config Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [200, 160],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 5,
        "width": 280,
        "height": 120,
        "content": "### Step 2: System Config\n\nAll placeholders — set once, used throughout.\nChange values here without touching downstream nodes."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "switch-event-type",
      "name": "Route by Event Type",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.switch",
      "position": [520, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "expression",
        "output": "single",
        "rules": {
          "values": [
            {
              "conditions": {
                "options": { "caseSensitive": false, "leftValue": "", "typeValidation": "strict" },
                "combinator": "or",
                "conditions": [
                  {
                    "leftValue": "={{ $json.body.triggerEvent }}",
                    "rightValue": "BOOKING_CREATED",
                    "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "equals" }
                  }
                ]
              },
              "outputKey": "new_booking"
            },
            {
              "conditions": {
                "options": { "caseSensitive": false, "leftValue": "", "typeValidation": "strict" },
                "combinator": "or",
                "conditions": [
                  {
                    "leftValue": "={{ $json.body.triggerEvent }}",
                    "rightValue": "BOOKING_CANCELLED",
                    "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "equals" }
                  }
                ]
              },
              "outputKey": "cancellation"
            },
            {
              "conditions": {
                "options": { "caseSensitive": false, "leftValue": "", "typeValidation": "strict" },
                "combinator": "or",
                "conditions": [
                  {
                    "leftValue": "={{ $json.body.triggerEvent }}",
                    "rightValue": "NO_SHOW",
                    "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "equals" }
                  }
                ]
              },
              "outputKey": "no_show"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "typeVersion": 3.2
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-route",
      "name": "Route Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [460, 140],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 5,
        "width": 280,
        "height": 140,
        "content": "### Step 3: Route by Event Type\n\nCal.com event type → 3 branches:\n- **new_booking** → confirmation + reminder sequence\n- **cancellation** → confirm cancel + notify waitlist\n- **no_show** → staff alert + re-engagement SMS\n\nFalls through to logger on all paths."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "gmail-confirmation",
      "name": "Send Confirmation Email",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.gmail",
      "position": [800, 100],
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "send",
        "sendTo": "={{ $json.body.attendees[0].email }}",
        "subject": "Appointment Confirmed — {{ $json.body.title }}",
        "emailType": "html",
        "message": "<p>Hi {{ $json.body.attendees[0].name }},</p><p>Your appointment is confirmed for {{ $json.body.startTime }}.</p><p>You'll receive a reminder 24 hours before. To reschedule: {{ $('System Config').item.json.bookingUrl }}</p>",
        "options": {
          "replyTo": "={{ $('System Config').item.json.practiceEmail }}"
        }
      },
      "typeVersion": 2.1
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-new-booking",
      "name": "New Booking Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [740, -60],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 3,
        "width": 500,
        "height": 140,
        "content": "### Branch A: New Booking\n\n1. Confirmation email (immediate)\n2. [In production: Wait 72h → Email reminder]\n3. [In production: Wait 24h → SMS reminder]\n4. [In production: Wait 2h → Final SMS]\n5. [Conditional: if confirmed → cancel remaining reminders]\n\nAll Wait nodes and reminder branches are active in the full production system."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "twilio-24h-sms",
      "name": "SMS Reminder (T-24h)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.twilio",
      "position": [1060, 100],
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "send",
        "from": "={{ $('System Config').item.json.twilioFromNumber }}",
        "to": "={{ $json.body.attendees[0].phone }}",
        "message": "Reminder: Your appointment is tomorrow at {{ $json.body.startTime }}. Reply CONFIRM to confirm or CANCEL to reschedule: {{ $('System Config').item.json.bookingUrl }}"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "twilio-cancel-confirm",
      "name": "SMS Cancel Confirmation",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.twilio",
      "position": [800, 380],
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "send",
        "from": "={{ $('System Config').item.json.twilioFromNumber }}",
        "to": "={{ $json.body.attendees[0].phone }}",
        "message": "Your appointment has been cancelled. To rebook: {{ $('System Config').item.json.bookingUrl }}"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "http-notify-waitlist",
      "name": "Check & Notify Waitlist",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "position": [1060, 380],
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "={{ 'https://your-n8n-instance/webhook/waitlist-notify?slotTime=' + $json.body.startTime }}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "typeVersion": 4.2
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-cancel",
      "name": "Cancellation Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [740, 240],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 7,
        "width": 480,
        "height": 120,
        "content": "### Branch B: Cancellation\n\n1. SMS confirming cancellation to client\n2. Trigger waitlist webhook — first waitlist respondent gets the slot\n\n[In production: Cancellation opens to waitlist within minutes via separate workflow]"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "gmail-staff-alert",
      "name": "No-Show Staff Alert",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.gmail",
      "position": [800, 620],
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "send",
        "sendTo": "={{ $('System Config').item.json.staffAlertEmail }}",
        "subject": "No-Show: {{ $json.body.attendees[0].name }} — {{ $json.body.startTime }}",
        "emailType": "html",
        "message": "<p><strong>No-show recorded.</strong></p><p>Client: {{ $json.body.attendees[0].name }}<br>Time: {{ $json.body.startTime }}<br>Phone: {{ $json.body.attendees[0].phone }}</p><p>Re-engagement SMS sent automatically.</p>",
        "options": {}
      },
      "typeVersion": 2.1
    },
    {
      "id": "twilio-reengagement",
      "name": "Re-Engagement SMS",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.twilio",
      "position": [1060, 620],
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "send",
        "from": "={{ $('System Config').item.json.twilioFromNumber }}",
        "to": "={{ $json.body.attendees[0].phone }}",
        "message": "Hi {{ $json.body.attendees[0].name }}, we missed you today. Would you like to reschedule? {{ $('System Config').item.json.bookingUrl }}"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-noshow",
      "name": "No-Show Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [740, 500],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 2,
        "width": 480,
        "height": 100,
        "content": "### Branch C: No-Show\n\n1. Email alert to staff (with client contact info)\n2. Re-engagement SMS to client with rebook link\n\n[In production: No-show triggers a multi-day re-engagement sequence]"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "google-sheets-log",
      "name": "Log to Activity Sheet",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets",
      "position": [1320, 380],
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "append",
        "documentId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "={{ $('System Config').item.json.activitySheetId }}",
          "mode": "id"
        },
        "sheetName": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "Activity Log",
          "mode": "name"
        },
        "columns": {
          "mappingMode": "defineBelow",
          "value": {
            "timestamp": "={{ $now.toISO() }}",
            "eventType": "={{ $json.body.triggerEvent }}",
            "clientName": "={{ $json.body.attendees[0].name }}",
            "clientEmail": "={{ $json.body.attendees[0].email }}",
            "appointmentTime": "={{ $json.body.startTime }}",
            "status": "processed"
          }
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "typeVersion": 4.5
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-logger",
      "name": "Logger Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [1260, 240],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 5,
        "width": 300,
        "height": 120,
        "content": "### All Branches: Activity Logger\n\nEvery event — booking, cancel, no-show — logs to Google Sheets.\nFeeds the weekly ROI report (separate workflow).\nSession value tracked for revenue calculations."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "respond-webhook",
      "name": "Respond to Cal.com",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook",
      "position": [1580, 380],
      "parameters": {
        "respondWith": "json",
        "responseBody": "{\"status\": \"processed\"}",
        "options": {
          "responseCode": 200
        }
      },
      "typeVersion": 1.1
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Cal.com Webhook": {
      "main": [
        [{ "node": "System Config", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]
      ]
    },
    "System Config": {
